name: ONE of ONE of ONE | ISSUE 4/4
description:
this is your wallet identifier represented by a series of seemingly random glyphs across a single, static colour, with absolutely no variance in hue, saturation or luminosity

focus on the characters within and try to remember the frame of mind you were in when you last hit a problem so difficult to solve it almost literally broke your brain; look back to this time and compare it against your current situation - do you see the contrast now?

this unique 1/1 goes a step further by adding an additional dimension, ensuring each viewer has their own unique, persistent version of this nft, essentially turning it into a 1/1/1 edition
